Package: qfwr
Type: Package
Title: Tutorials for "Quantitative Finance with R" course
Version: 0.1.02
Author: Yongyi Zeng
Maintainer: Yongyi Zeng <zzyy@xmu.edu.cn>
Description: Tutorials for my course "Quantitative Finance with R" 
    (QFwR) to facilitate teaching and learning. The interactive 
    exercise is mainly powered by RStudio's `learnr`, `gradethis` 
    package and some ideas / codes stolen from Prof. Rundel's 
    `learnrhash`.
